event title: Intangible Form and Night Trade at Rising 2025
event description: Start your night in a trance and end it in the beating heart of Rising with these two free events at the historic Capitol building.
From dance-floor communions to a competition where doing nothing is the main event, Rising’s free program this year is as bold and boundary-pushing as ever.

event title: Pre-Screening of Wes Anderson’s The Phoenician Scheme
event description: Be among the first to see Wes Anderson’s latest pastel-hued, star-studded film with Broadsheet Access. Members can catch a private pre-screening in Melbourne and Sydney this May, with complimentary drinks and snacks on arrival.
